## 1. 代码逻辑

- 当插入订单时，不小于库存才可以插入；

-  插入后，对products 表同时更新库存

```sql
create trigger update_qty on orders

instead of insert
as

begin transaction

set transaction isolation level read committed

declare @amount float

set @amount = 
(select quantity from products where pid=(select pid from inserted)) - (select qty from inserted)

if (@amount >= 0)
begin
-- 插入
insert into orders select * from inserted
-- 更新库存
update products set quantity=@amount
where pid=(select pid from inserted)
end

else
print 'Fail to insert!'

commit
```
